title: Proxmox VE: Node LVM Storages
agents: proxmox_ve
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the storage usage of LVM-based storage on Proxmox VE nodes.
 It reports disk space usage, free space, and utilization percentages for each LVM
 storage configured as storage in Proxmox VE.
 LVM storages are storage backends of type "lvm" or "lvm-thin".

discovery:
 One service per LVM storage is created.
